<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">The books aren&apos;t related in any way, so you can read either one first, depending upon what you&apos;re in the mood to read. I read Uprooted first and loved<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">The books aren't related in any way, so you can read either one first, depending upon what you're in the mood to read. I read Uprooted first and loved it, and now I'm starting in on this series which has a completely different feel, but seems well written, too. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
